title: Ceph Storage: Classes
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the size and used space of pools of Ceph storage systems by their class.

 The usage is checked against values configurable using the ruleset "Filesystems (used space and growth)".

item:
 The pools classes.

discovery:
 One service is created for each pool class.

cluster:
 On a cluster only the first nodes' response is checked.
